uding consideration of bronchoscopy with bronchoalveolar lavage (BAL) if clinically indicated.", "intention": "diagnostic", "priority": 2}, {"action": "Monitor **vital signs, fluid status, and urine output** closely, with consideration for ICU transfer if respiratory status deteriorates.", "intention": "supportive", "priority": 2}, {"action": "Review and adjust **immunosuppressive regimen** in consultation with transplant team to balance infection risk and cGvHD control.", "intention": "therapeutic", "priority": 3}]}}}
